name: Villa Dukuh
address: Nyambu, Kediri, Tabanan Regency, Bali 82121, Indonesia
review 1:
A return trip to the beautiful Villa Dukuh. A great relaxing holiday with our family. The online photos are great but the villa is even better in reality.
Close to everything by a short drive but also set apart so you can enjoy the peace and quiet of the local rice field surrounds. Great meals by the villa staff who also organised a great bike tour of the area. Beautiful infinity pool and tennis court.
Love this place!
review 2: We loved our holiday at Villa Dukuh.  The staff were very attentive and did everything to make our stay a wonderful balinese experience.  The food was amazing and the accommodation was beautiful.  The staff went out of their way for us and it was very sad to say good-bye.  Well worth a visit in a lovely village with beautiful staff from that village.
